---
title: Red Pesto & Green Bean Risotto with Lemon & Garlic Pangrattato
description: Our red pesto – made with chargrilled capsicum, sun-dried tomatoes, parmesan, basil and garlic – puts a fun twist on this veggie risotto. Sprinkle it with a lemon and garlic breadcrumb pangrattato for a burst of citrusy freshness and you’ve got a dinner that delivers with every mouthful.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5d2feed5ec3685000e69b116-0a0d5663.jpg
